{"tid":408047,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「腹語女」Darci大熱姿態《全美一叮》奪冠","createTime":"2017-09-21T02:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-23T03:53:53.000Z","uid":94075,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdf99ee503f6139c36df745987bd7e529a737123","tid":408047,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T02:10:59.000Z","msg":"美國才藝比賽真人騷《全美一叮》（America's Got Talent，AGT）剛公布賽果，結果連月來一直被視為冠軍頂頭大熱的12歲天才「腹語女」Darci Lynne擊敗「小雲妮」之稱的Angelica Hale而勇奪冠軍，成功拎走780萬港元獎金！<br />\nDarci昨日在《全》現場表演時技驚四座「一拖二」以「鼠男兔女」Oscar與Petunia兩個布偶出戰，以難度極高的腹語秘技唱出樂隊披頭四（The Beatles）的經典名曲《With A Little Help From My Friends》，贏盡現場觀眾掌聲之餘，亦獲兩位評判Heidi Klum與Simon Cowell大讚「sure win」。<br />\n<br />\n至於僅次於Darci獲亞軍的就是現年10歲、有「小雲妮侯斯頓」之稱的Angelica Hale，雖然最終仍以熱門姿態落敗，但仍好有風度與Darci相擁落淚，絕對是輸了比賽但贏了友誼！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170921/bkn-20170921100124659-0921_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170921%2Fbkn-20170921100124659-0921_00862_001.html&d=W%2BDrk0pFq8X8upnLo%2Bi4jP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=0fd3d759\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170921/bkn-20170921100124659-0921_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d3d5029ce2d730495a9c7c8a8b675b17b484b161","tid":408047,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T04:08:15.000Z","msg":"No one cares about Celine and her father"},{"pid":"1cd996255e0522a87dbbbd06798b5136d4485afd","tid":408047,"uid":9747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-21T08:56:44.000Z","msg":"好撚勁<br />\n同時扮2個聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224c8cdd2ce2f401b8a70c6ab611c19dc8289e96","tid":408047,"uid":2509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-23T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}